561
00:25:51,708 --> 00:25:52,625
Nothing.

562
00:25:52,791 --> 00:25:53,875
You can have my meal.

563
00:25:54,416 --> 00:25:55,416
It's okay.

564
00:26:00,625 --> 00:26:03,583
Excuse me, sir.
Can I have an extra one, please?

565
00:26:04,791 --> 00:26:06,291
One for each person.

566
00:26:06,375 --> 00:26:08,333
You are just an extra.
Don't be so greedy all the time.

567
00:26:08,541 --> 00:26:09,500
Get lost.

568
00:26:11,291 --> 00:26:12,166
Get lost.

569
00:26:14,125 --> 00:26:16,583
If you dare to come back,
I'll call the cops.

570
00:26:19,666 --> 00:26:21,333
