577
00:26:32,375 --> 00:26:33,291
Answer me.

578
00:26:33,916 --> 00:26:35,583
What is it? What answer do you want?

579
00:26:37,833 --> 00:26:40,208
Aren't those lunch boxes for eating?

580
00:26:40,333 --> 00:26:41,416
Yes, so what?

581
00:26:41,500 --> 00:26:43,750
