with a bottle?

589
00:27:10,708 --> 00:27:11,833
I couldn't hit him, could I?

590
00:27:11,916 --> 00:27:13,375
Didn't you see how big he was?

591
00:27:14,791 --> 00:27:15,916
You are indeed...

592
00:27:22,583 --> 00:27:23,958
