We can dub the lines later.

753
00:37:42,833 --> 00:37:44,208
You're letting me count the numbers?

754
00:37:44,291 --> 00:37:45,208
Are you insulting me?

755
00:37:45,291 --> 00:37:46,750
No, this is easier.

756
00:37:46,833 --> 00:37:48,833
