757
00:37:48,916 --> 00:37:50,875
You wasted my time, you damn fool.

758
00:37:50,958 --> 00:37:52,666
Come on, shoot.

759
00:37:53,750 --> 00:37:54,666
Ready.

760
00:37:56,875 --> 00:37:58,500
One, two, three...

761
00:38:01,375 --> 00:38:03,958
- One, two, three, four, five, six...
- One, two, three, four, five, six...

762
00:38:04,041 --> 00:38:06,166
Got it. Roll.

763
00:38:07,083 --> 00:38:09,625
One, two, three, four, five, six...

764
00:38:09,708 --> 00:38:10,625
Eight...

765
00:38:12,791 --> 00:38:16,041
- One, two, three, four, five, six...
- One, two, three, four, five, six...

766
00:38:16,166 --> 00:38:17,083
Who wrote these lines?

767
00:38:17,166 --> 00:38:19,125
It doesn't make any sense.
How can I memorize this?

768
00:38:20,541 --> 00:38:22,333
My Chinese is not good.
Let's do it in English.

769
00:38:22,416 --> 00:38:23,666
Okay. Ready.

770
00:38:51,833 --> 00:38:52,916
What is he doing?

771
00:38:59,291 --> 00:39:01,166
Mr. Marco, what's wrong with you?

772
00:39:02,250 --> 00:39:04,125
Can't you understand simple English?

773
00:39:04,208 --> 00:39:05,125
No, I don't.

774
00:39:05,208 --> 00:39:06,375
And the way you were doing it...

775
00:39:06,583 --> 00:39:08,916
Of course, you won't understand.
But if you insist, I'll tell you.

776
00:39:09,166 --> 00:39:10,041
Attention, everyone.

777
00:39:10,125 --> 00:39:12,458
Mr. Marco is giving acting lessons.
Something amazing is happening.

778
00:39:12,541 --> 00:39:15,416
I killed my beloved by myself.

779
00:39:15,500 --> 00:39:17,958
My emotions are extremely complicated.

780
00:39:18,250 --> 00:39:22,958
Sad, fear, selfish, vanity, arrogant,
excited, shy and so on.

781
00:39:23,208 --> 00:39:24,916
Those emotions...

782
