how you made your comeback?

1288
01:05:56,625 --> 01:05:57,750
What "comeback"?

1289
01:05:58,125 --> 01:05:59,791
You're popular once again.

1290
01:05:59,916 --> 01:06:01,708
No, I was asking you
what do you mean by "comeback"?

1291
01:06:01,833 --> 01:06:02,708
I...

1292
01:06:02,791 --> 01:06:04,458
- Was I dead or disappear?
- I didn't mean...

1293
01:06:04,541 --> 01:06:06,250
I'm sorry. I didn't mean it that way.

1294
01:06:06,333 --> 01:06:08,416
No, what did you mean by "comeback"?

1295
01:06:08,958 --> 01:06:10,416
Are you trying to insult me?

1296
01:06:14,333 --> 01:06:17,083
- Your acting was really good.
- Of course.

1297
01:06:17,625 --> 01:06:20,291
Mr. Marco is absolutely brilliant.
Your emotions can appear anytime.

1298
01:06:20,416 --> 01:06:23,416
Sure, when my emotions overflow,
it is unstoppable.

1299
01:06:23,500 --> 01:06:26,833
Can you show us
the "peeing-the-pants" look again?

1300
01:06:30,666 --> 01:06:33,625
<i>I think that many children will be
watching this program.</i>

1301
01:06:33,708 --> 01:06:34,708
<i>Let's not do that.</i>

1302
01:06:34,791 --> 01:06:37,416
<i>You're right. Do you have
any upcoming plans?</i>

1303
01:06:37,541 --> 01:06:40,416
<i>I've got many invitations
to take part in the international films.</i>

1304
01:06:40,500 --> 01:06:42,416
- I've met Mr. Marco.
<i>- Like thriller...</i>

1305
01:06:42,541 --> 01:06:44,500
This is the video of me
scaring him to pee his pants.

1306
01:06:44,708 --> 01:06:45,708
You're an actor too?

1307
01:06:45,833 --> 01:06:48,083
Yes, I used to be an actor.

1308
01:06:48,291 --> 01:06:49,791
Have you met Bruce Lee?

1309
01:06:49,875 --> 01:06:51,291
- I've met...
- Hey.

1310
01:06:51,833 --> 01:06:54,291
Stop chatting and get back to work.

1311
01:06:55,541 --> 01:06:57,708
<i>There were so many ups and downs
in your life.</i>

1312
01:06:58,083 --> 01:06:59,250
<i>Tell us how you feel.</i>

1313
01:06:59,833 --> 01:07:01,750
<i>I feel so blessed.</i>

1314
01:07:01,833 --> 01:07:04,958
<i>Not everyone has this kind of experience.</i>

1315
01:07:07,166 --> 01:07:10,208
<i>I am grateful to the person
who scared me in the video.</i>

1316
01:07:10,666 --> 01:07:12,541
<i>I wouldn't be here today without her.</i>

1317
01:07:12,916 --> 01:07:14,041
<i>Who is she?</i>

1318
01:07:14,291 --> 01:07:16,291
I don't know her name, but...

1319
01:07:16,916 --> 01:07:17,833
She is an actor.

1320
01:07:21,250 --> 01:07:22,333
Dreamy.

1321
01:07:22,875 --> 01:07:24,583
Look who's here.

1322
01:07:25,875 --> 01:07:28,666
- You are so handsome today.
- Yes.

1323
01:07:28,916 --> 01:07:30,958
- Mr. Marco.
- Yes, Mr. Marco.

1324
01:07:31,041 --> 01:07:33,208
Dreamy, I've finally found you.

1325
01:07:33,333 --> 01:07:34,500
I come all the way to thank you.

1326
01:07:34,583 --> 01:07:37,416
Actually, she didn't do much.
All she did was scared you.

1327
01:07:37,666 --> 01:07:39,625
My hair turned white
from the shock she brought me.

1328
01:07:39,708 --> 01:07:41,416
I wouldn't thank her for that.

1329
01:07:41,875 --> 01:07:43,666
- Have a seat, please.
- It smells delicious.

1330
01:07:43,750 --> 01:07:46,250
Mr. Marco, you're so popular now.

1331
01:07:46,708 --> 01:07:48,416
It's all thanks to your scary face.

1332
01:07:48,500 --> 01:07:49,750
You have an amazing daughter.

1333
01:07:49,833 --> 01:07:51,666
- You're way too kind.
- She looks like her dad.

1334
01:07:51,750 --> 01:07:53,333
- No, like her mom.
- Looks like her dad.

1335
01:07:53,458 --> 01:07:55,375
- Looks like her mom.
- She looks like both of you.

1336
01:07:56,500 --> 01:07:57,791
Also, I want to congratulate you.

1337
01:07:57,875 --> 01:08:00,583
You're on the list
for Stephen Chow's new movie.

1338
01:08:01,208 --> 01:08:02,125
What?

1339
01:08:02,625 --> 01:08:03,583
You didn't know?

1340
01:08:04,083 --> 01:08:06,791
They're recruiting new actors
with real talent.

1341
01:08:06,875 --> 01:08:08,250
I saw your name on the list.

1342
01:08:08,333 --> 01:08:09,333
Where did you see it?

1343
01:08:09,541 --> 01:08:10,750
I found it online.

1344
01:08:11,375 --> 01:08:13,125
It's held in Beijing tomorrow.
See, right here.

1345
01:08:15,833 --> 01:08:17,166
- What happened to the Internet?
- Sorry.

1346
01:08:17,250 --> 01:08:18,833
It's fine, I'm not going.

1347
01:08:19,666 --> 01:08:20,541
Why not?

1348
01:08:20,625 --> 01:08:22,041
I have a new job now.

1349
01:08:22,208 --> 01:08:23,375
I am not an actor anymore.

1350
01:08:23,833 --> 01:08:26,750
- Why not?
- I'm a waitress now.

1351
01:08:27,000 --> 01:08:29,708
Plus, I'm operating an online shop
and making a decent living.

1352
01:08:29,833 --> 01:08:31,166
Dad and Mom are satisfied.

1353
01:08:31,250 --> 01:08:33,625
Yes. Dreamy is living
a happy and stable life.

1354
01:08:33,750 --> 01:08:35,583
- This is good for her.
- Yes, it is.

1355
01:08:36,208 --> 01:08:37,833
- Here, Mr. Marco.
- Yes.

1356
01:08:38,333 --> 01:08:39,541
It's a good thing.

1357
01:08:40,416 --> 01:08:41,458
It's good.

1358
01:08:42,416 --> 01:08:43,375
What's the matter?

1359
01:08:45,750 --> 01:08:47,625
- I'm just not feeling well.
- Is it menopause?

1360
01:08:47,791 --> 01:08:49,583
Nonsense. He is way too young.

1361
01:08:49,666 --> 01:08:51,041
Is it a heart attack?

1362
01:08:51,125 --> 01:08:53,125
- Quick, call the ambulance.
- No need. I'm okay.

1363
01:08:53,208 --> 01:08:54,500
- It could be serious.
- I'm fine.

1364
01:08:54,583 --> 01:08:56,416
Seeing Dreamy living a good life,

1365
01:08:56,500 --> 01:08:58,208
I'm feeling quite sad.

1366
01:09:02,166 --> 01:09:03,500
Don't get me wrong.

1367
01:09:03,708 --> 01:09:05,583
What I meant was

1368
01:09:05,750 --> 01:09:10,916
it's like an undefeatable boxer
giving up before the match even starts.

1369
01:09:11,250 --> 01:09:14,291
I didn't give up,
but I just came to my senses.

1370
01:09:14,833 --> 01:09:16,375
I don't fantasize
about being a star anymore.

1371
01:09:16,750 --> 01:09:17,916
You're giving up.

1372
01:09:20,416 --> 01:09:21,416
Mr. Marco.

1373
01:09:22,333 --> 01:09:23,708
It has been more than a decade.

1374
01:09:24,833 --> 01:09:27,375
I was ridiculed and rejected every day.

1375
01:09:28,666 --> 01:09:30,583
Nobody wanted to see me acting.

1376
01:09:32,250 --> 01:09:34,416
I've never gotten
a single moment of respect.

1377
01:09:35,125 --> 01:09:36,291
I've had enough.

1378
01:09:36,791 --> 01:09:37,625
Why?

1379
01:09:38,916 --> 01:09:40,041
What do you mean by that?

1380
01:09:40,416 --> 01:09:41,625
Why did you give up?

1381
01:09:42,000 --> 01:09:43,125
This is not giving up.

1382
01:09:43,333 --> 01:09:44,291
It's just...

1383
01:09:45,125 --> 01:09:47,291
It's just that I'm not cut out for it.

1384
01:09:47,583 --> 01:09:50,041
Hard work doesn't always pay off.

1385
01:09:50,708 --> 01:09:53,291
I told you so, but you insisted.

1386
01:09:53,416 --> 01:09:55,625
Let her be. She was bullied all the time.

1387
01:09:56,333 --> 01:09:57,875
I know, I get it.

1388
01:09:58,166 --> 01:09:59,666
I totally understand.

1389
01:10:00,125 --> 01:10:03,875
I came here just to show my gratitude.

1390
01:10:04,500 --> 01:10:06,125
I have something to do. I've got to go.

1391
01:10:06,291 --> 01:10:07,541
Let's finish the meal first.

1392
01:10:07,625 --> 01:10:09,333
Mr. Marco, have dinner before you leave.

1393
01:10:09,500 --> 01:10:10,625
Yes, Mr. Marco.

1394
01:10:11,750 --> 01:10:14,875
I think that success
is all about not giving up.

1395
01:10:15,625 --> 01:10:17,166
You taught me that.

1396
01:10:40,125 --> 01:10:42,875
- Maybe I should give it a try...
- I knew you will be like this.

1397
01:10:43,375 --> 01:10:45,041
You useless bum.

1398
01:10:45,541 --> 01:10:47,166
Go.

1399
01:10:47,291 --> 01:10:48,875
- Book her a ticket.
- Hey.

1400
01:10:49,458 --> 01:10:50,833
Train or plane?

1401
01:10:50,916 --> 01:10:52,500
- Plane.
- Got it.

1402
01:10:52,583 --> 01:10:53,916
- First class.
- Yes.

1403
01:10:54,791 --> 01:10:55,666
Get out of here.

1404
01:10:58,958 --> 01:11:00,291
I don't need that much, Dad.

1405
01:11:00,541 --> 01:11:03,791
Take it. You're just a bum.

1406
01:11:03,875 --> 01:11:05,291
- Let me tell you...
- I've got the tickets.

1407
01:11:05,375 --> 01:11:07,125
- Go now.
- Is it first class?

1408
01:11:09,833 --> 01:11:11,000
- Thank you, Mom.
- Okay.

1409
01:11:11,541 --> 01:11:12,583
Dad, you're the best.

1410
01:11:14,166 --> 01:11:16,875
- Silly girl, don't ever come back.
- All right.

1411
01:11:16,958 --> 01:11:19,041
- Did you take the house keys?
- I got it.

1412
01:11:20,416 --> 01:11:23,500
BODY MOVEMENT

1413
01:11:39,916 --> 01:11:41,000
I'm a robot.

1414
01:11:41,083 --> 01:11:42,208
Thank you, next.

1415
01:11:44,750 --> 01:11:45,666
Good day, judges.

1416
01:11:50,958 --> 01:11:54,208
I'm a growing mushroom.

1417
01:11:54,375 --> 01:11:55,416
- It has...
- Okay, next.

1418
01:11:56,458 --> 01:11:58,958
Hurry up. Next.

1419
01:11:59,166 --> 01:12:00,916
EMOTIONAL CONTROL

1420
01:12:01,000 --> 01:12:01,916
Mom!

1421
01:12:02,333 --> 01:12:04,375
Grandpa! Grandma!

1422
01:12:04,708 --> 01:12:07,083
Uncle! Cousin!

1423
01:12:07,333 --> 01:12:08,708
Brother-in-law.

1424
01:12:09,291 --> 01:12:10,375
Aunt!

1425
01:12:13,375 --> 01:12:14,625
Why does this happen to me?

1426
01:12:25,125 --> 01:12:27,375
My whole family is dead.

1427
01:12:27,458 --> 01:12:29,166
Fantastic. Next.

1428
01:12:33,458 --> 01:12:34,333
Good day, judges.

1429
01:12:41,583 --> 01:12:43,791
Okay, next.

1430
01:12:43,875 --> 01:12:45,375
Sorry, please let me indulge myself.

1431
01:12:45,458 --> 01:12:47,000
- I just need five minutes.
- Hey!

1432
01:12:47,083 --> 01:12:49,708
Five minutes?
There are over a hundred people waiting.

1433
01:12:49,875 --> 01:12:52,125
TALENT SHOWCASE

1434
01:13:23,083 --> 01:13:24,166
Thank you.

1435
01:13:24,250 --> 01:13:25,916
That's very good. Next.

1436
01:13:29,958 --> 01:13:30,875
Good day, judges.

1437
01:13:33,041 --> 01:13:34,916
I can make sounds by my hands.

1438
01:13:36,166 --> 01:13:37,083
Next.

1439
01:13:37,833 --> 01:13:38,750
I'm sorry.

1440
01:13:40,000 --> 01:13:41,875
This is a talent showcase.

1441
01:13:42,750 --> 01:13:43,750
Idiot.

1442
01:13:44,125 --> 01:13:45,791
ROLE PLAY

1443
01:13:46,791 --> 01:13:48,833
Good day, judges. I will play a hero.

1444
01:13:48,916 --> 01:13:49,875
All right. Start.

1445
01:13:56,500 --> 01:13:59,250
I, Chen Zhen, will take revenge today.

1446
01:14:02,208 --> 01:14:04,291
Who killed my master?

1447
01:14:07,625 --> 01:14:08,666
Good day, judges.

1448
01:14:09,000 --> 01:14:10,291
I will play a spy.

1449
01:14:10,666 --> 01:14:11,708
All right. Get started.

1450
01:14:12,375 --> 01:14:15,458
Boss, what are you doing?
Aren't we supposed to be playing mahjong?

1451
01:14:15,541 --> 01:14:16,583
Don't.

1452
01:14:17,208 --> 01:14:19,708
Hey. Boss, it hurts.

1453
01:14:19,958 --> 01:14:21,333
Please don't use your belt.

1454
01:14:25,833 --> 01:14:27,750
- Good day, judges.
- Hurry up.

1455
01:14:28,416 --> 01:14:29,750
I play a con man.

1456
01:14:30,416 --> 01:14:31,333
Go ahead.

1457
01:14:33,791 --> 01:14:36,875
- Hurry. There are over a hundred people.
- Darling.

1458
01:14:38,541 --> 01:14:39,791
Hey.

1459
01:14:40,041 --> 01:14:42,541
Darling, she is my cousin.
Wait for me for a while.

1460
01:14:48,375 --> 01:14:49,666
Who is she?

1461
01:14:50,458 --> 01:14:51,375
A client.

1462
01:14:51,625 --> 01:14:53,333
Why did you call me your cousin?

1463
01:14:53,750 --> 01:14:56,416
Whatever. Don't worry about it.

1464
01:14:56,666 --> 01:14:58,791
- Let me ask her.
- Don't.

1465
01:15:00,125 --> 01:15:03,000
She is really my client
and you're my client too.

1466
01:15:03,291 --> 01:15:05,666
I provide services, do you get it?

1467
01:15:05,958 --> 01:15:07,041
What kind of services?

1468
01:15:07,125 --> 01:15:08,541
Well...

1469
01:15:11,500 --> 01:15:12,958
Boyfriend for hire.

1470
01:15:13,166 --> 01:15:14,750
Are you an escort?

1471
01:15:15,083 --> 01:15:18,291
Whatever, it's the same thing.

1472
01:15:18,916 --> 01:15:20,250
Why me?

1473
01:15:20,958 --> 01:15:22,166
{\an8}Is it because I'm stupid?

1474
01:15:22,666 --> 01:15:25,625
Don't be so hard on yourself.

1475
01:15:27,958 --> 01:15:31,583
Ignorance is bliss. It makes you happier.

1476
01:15:35,583 --> 01:15:37,583
The money you need. I've got all you need.

1477
01:15:37,666 --> 01:15:39,333
If you want to lie to me,
I'll just let it be.

1478
01:15:39,875 --> 01:15:41,375
I'm not scamming you.

1479
01:15:41,666 --> 01:15:43,333
I'm just collecting my service fees.

1480
01:15:44,125 --> 01:15:48,041
You can't just dine and dash, right?

1481
01:15:49,416 --> 01:15:54,625
You never thought
I would make it as an actress, right?

1482
01:15:54,791 --> 01:15:55,958
You'll make it.

1483
01:15:56,041 --> 01:15:57,541
You're the very best.

1484
01:15:58,166 --> 01:16:02,500
As long as you pay me, I'll keep saying it
as often as you wish.

1485
01:16:04,708 --> 01:16:07,541
Don't cry. She'll get suspicious.

1486
01:16:13,583 --> 01:16:15,791
Don't screw it up for me.

1487
01:16:19,041 --> 01:16:22,833
Hey, I've asked you
to stop being a junkie.

1488
01:16:22,916 --> 01:16:24,125
It'll kill you.

1489
01:16:24,208 --> 01:16:27,041
It's never too late to turn it around.

1490
01:16:30,000 --> 01:16:30,916
Thank you.

1491
01:16:32,250 --> 01:16:33,958
Why did you hit me?

1492
01:16:34,250 --> 01:16:35,458
I'm not the cousin.

1493
01:16:35,958 --> 01:16:37,708
Sorry, I didn't mean that.

1494
01:16:39,500 --> 01:16:42,375
Can you switch the role
and be the victim now?

1495
01:16:42,791 --> 01:16:43,708
Sure.

1496
01:16:52,125 --> 01:16:53,541
Are you an escort?

1497
01:16:53,625 --> 01:16:56,250
Whatever, it's the same thing.

1498
01:16:59,666 --> 01:17:01,791
How could you do this?

1499
01:17:01,875 --> 01:17:05,208
Don't cry. She'll get suspicious.

1500
01:17:10,791 --> 01:17:12,750
You look like a retard.

1501
01:17:13,791 --> 01:17:15,875
How could you be an escort?

1502
01:17:16,625 --> 01:17:20,500
You can say anything about me,
but don't say I'm a retard.

1503
01:17:20,583 --> 01:17:22,458
That's not true.

1504
01:17:23,833 --> 01:17:25,541
I've touched your nerve, haven't I?

1505
01:17:26,166 --> 01:17:28,291
You must have been seen
as a retarded since young.

1506
01:17:28,458 --> 01:17:30,875
So now, you scam people
to boost your self-esteem.

1507
01:17:30,958 --> 01:17:33,541
That's bullshit.
Everyone loved me since I was a kid.

1508
01:17:33,625 --> 01:17:35,541
They didn't love you.
They just pitied you.

1509
01:17:35,625 --> 01:17:37,291
- Shut up.
- You shut up.

1510
01:17:37,750 --> 01:17:40,208
Someone like you
doesn't deserve to be loved.

1511
01:17:40,291 --> 01:17:41,125
I...

1512
01:17:44,208 --> 01:17:45,333
You lowlife.

1513
01:17:45,875 --> 01:17:47,541
Everyone loves you?

1514
01:17:47,791 --> 01:17:50,833
How could you be an escort with this face?
I'm going to kill you.

1515
01:17:54,083 --> 01:17:57,083
- Why did you do this again?
- My goodness. I'm so sorry.

1516
01:17:57,458 --> 01:17:59,208
I really didn't mean to hurt you.

1517
01:17:59,416 --> 01:18:01,583
All right. Enough. Next.

1518
01:18:03,083 --> 01:18:04,375
So sorry.

1519
01:18:07,291 --> 01:18:08,208
Hey.

1520
01:18:08,833 --> 01:18:11,250
That way. You're shortlisted.

1521
01:18:40,458 --> 01:18:44,541
ONE YEAR LATER

1522
01:18:53,708 --> 01:18:56,458
- Hey, what are you doing?
- We're here looking for our daughter.

1523
01:18:56,541 --> 01:18:58,916
Look for her at the police station.
There's an event tonight.

1524
01:19:03,500 --> 01:19:04,708
- Please go upstairs.
- Thank you.

1525
01:19:13,458 --> 01:19:16,625
I have all sorts of feelings
after hearing this song.

1526
01:19:16,833 --> 01:19:19,083
I wonder if everyone here
feels the same way.

1527
01:19:19,166 --> 01:19:20,958
- Over there.
- Okay, let's continue with the awards.

1528
01:19:21,041 --> 01:19:24,166
The competition for the best actress award
this year is intense.

1529
01:19:24,250 --> 01:19:30,083
The nominees are from all generations
in the Chinese movie industry.

1530
01:19:30,208 --> 01:19:32,375
Who'll win the crown
of today's best actress award?

1531
01:19:32,458 --> 01:19:36,541
Prior to that, let's enjoy the footages
before they became famous.

1532
01:19:40,458 --> 01:19:42,583
Lin Yun was quite pretty before.

1533
01:19:43,916 --> 01:19:44,750
Yes.

1534
01:19:47,541 --> 01:19:48,791
Who's that?

1535
01:19:51,041 --> 01:19:52,291
That's Dreamy.

1536
01:19:52,625 --> 01:19:53,583
You're right.

1537
01:21:12,750 --> 01:21:15,166
Please welcome
our award presenters on stage.

1538
01:21:20,833 --> 01:21:24,166
